Steps for installing express

Step1: Initializing node project using command "npm init"
Step2: installing express using command "npm install express"
step3: Create a file  ".gitingore" to ignore files those do not want to push in git. Add the library name.
Step4: Change the default js type into js6-->"type":"module" in package.json.
Step5: Create a file index.js and write the program to initailize a port
    a. First add the express library using import keyword.
    b. Use the imported express to initialize the port.(Check the steps in index.js) 

Closing the port using command Ctrl+c

