REST API

* REpresentational State Transfer
* Way to access web serrvices in a simple & flexible way
* HTTP methods used in rest
    1.GET  -->Read
    2.POST -->Create
    3.PUT --->Update
    4.DELETE-->Delete

Steps for Signup Postman

step1 : Create an account and signin postman
step2 : Using get method to send response to the server
step3 : Using post method to send request from the server 

